  <lyrics>[V1]
 Naya sapaquítwa Diosamajja
 Janiw yakha diosjja lurasi'tati.
 Jan Diosan sutipjja ina ch'usat
 Jupar ñankhachasa aynakasimti.
 
[C]
  Diosaw mandamiento? churistojja
 Aruparjamaya sarnakañáni.
 Criston munañapa lurañáni,
 Jupamp cusisita jacañataqui.
 
[V2]
 Amtasitaw Diosan urupatjja
 Jupan sutiparu jach'achañatac.
 Awquimar taycamar honrátawa,
 Jake masimarus jan jiwayamti.
 
[V3]
 Adulterio juchjja jan luramti,
 Janirac jumajja lunthatasimti.
 Jake masimatjja janiraquiw
 C'ari arunacjja parlasi'tati.
 
[V4]
 Jan masiman cuna yánacapsa
 Chuymamanjja munapayarakamti.
 Cristo saparuquiw munátajja
 Take chuymamampi, luráwimampi.
 
</lyrics></song>